ths have not been the smoothest for thesinger-songwriter, with reports of her marriage being in tatters, which has led to an allegeddivorcefrom her husband.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last few months\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"thesinger-songwriter\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"her marriage\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"tatters\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But speaking to this publication, Bucie was rather cagey about speaking on the state of her marriage.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bucie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this publication\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"her marriage\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never discussed the state of my marriage publicly, even though South Africans felt it was okay to speculate about it.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"my marriage\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"South Africans\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a sacred part of my life that I do not bring into the entertainment space.\\\"\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sacred part\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"the entertainment space\", \"fr